  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_revised_international_prognostic_index">Revised International Prognostic Index</xref>
 (
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_revised_international_prognostic_index">R-IPI</xref>
) is an 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_assessment_tool">ASSESSMENT TOOL</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_revised_international_prognostic_index">Revised International Prognostic Index</xref>
 is used to determine prognosis in 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 with Diffuse Large B-cell Lymphoma (DLBCL).  </p>
  <p>
For further information on the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_revised_international_prognostic_index">Revised International Prognostic Index</xref>
, see the 
    <xref href="https://qxmd.com/calculate/calculator_64/diffuse-large-b-cell-lymphoma-prognosis-r-ipi"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Revised International Prognostic Index calculator</xref>
.  </p>

